        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "加氢脱氧反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrodeoxygenation reaction",
        "description": "在200°C和30 bar氢气压力下，于间歇反应器中使用一系列双功能催化剂（铂负载在沸石H-Beta-25或H-Beta-300上，并以Bindzil作为粘合剂）进行异丁子香酚的加氢脱氧反应，以生产可再生航空燃料。研究了催化剂酸强度、金属纳米颗粒位置及其与酸位点接近度的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "Hydrodeoxygenation (HDO) of isoeugenol was carried out at 200 °C and 30 bar of H2 in a batch reactor using a series of bifunctional catalysts consisting of platinum supported on zeolite H-Beta-25 or H-Beta-300 and Bindzil as a binder.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
